detail.name: Great Saiyaman!
detail.effect: [Activate Main] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with a cost less than or equal to the number of cards with 《Satan City》 in their special traits in your Battle Area, and place it at the bottom of its owner's deck.
